'''Galma''' was a blood-red fruit that [[Rodian/Legends|Rodians]] ate as a breakfast food. It smelled faintly like a sweaty [[Bantha/Legends|bantha]], and was not appetizing to most other species. Rodian merchant [[Teeloo]] cooked it for breakfast for him and his friend before racing through [[Eskaron]] in [[33 BBY/Legends|33 BBY]].

